    <!-- Page Title -->
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Equipment</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8">
        Even though all territories might not subscribe to a system of currency, 
        or may have their own internal system, there is a universal currency that 
        is typically accepted at all places in the form of digital credits. 
        Physical money no longer exists, but many items can also often be created 
        with foraged supplies and successful Mechanics checks, or traded for.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8">
        All characters start with basic necessities - clothes suitable for 
        their environment/background, basic everyday supplies, a modest dwelling 
        of a sort appropriate to the environment, etc.


    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8">
        Backgrounds start with an additional three pieces of specific gear for 
        characters.
    </p>
    
